specifications: The MSI 15.6" GS66 Stealth Gaming Laptop is built for users that want a system that doesn't compromise on performance or portability. To keep up with graphically intensive gaming and even content creation on the side, this system is equipped with a 2.2 GHz Intel Core i7-10870H Eight-Core processor, 16GB of DDR4 RAM, a 1TB NVMe PCIe M.2 SSD, and an NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3070 graphics card. Its display measures 15.6" and has a 1920 x 1080 Full HD resolution. Additionally, it has a fast 300 Hz refresh rate for fluid gaming. Users can connect external displays using its HDMI and Thunderbolt 3 ports, as well as extra storage solutions and peripherals with its USB Type-A ports.
